# 0. Simple Web Stack

Domain: foobar.com
www record -> 8.8.8.8

Components:
- 1 Server
- Web Server (Nginx)
- Application Server
- Application Code Base
- Database (MySQL)

Explanation:
- Server: A machine that hosts the website
- Domain Name: Maps a name to an IP address
- DNS Record: www is an A record
- Web Server: Handles HTTP requests and serves static content
- Application Server: Runs backend logic
- Database: Stores application data
- Communication: HTTP/HTTPS over TCP/IP

Issues:
- SPOF (Single Point of Failure)
- Downtime during maintenance
- Cannot scale with high traffic
